---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for WooCommerce Stores — Product Testimonials That Drive Sales | SocialProof" description="Add real customer testimonials to your WooCommerce store. Boost product page conversions with social proof that builds trust at the moment of purchase.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for WooCommerce Stores
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Shoppers abandon WooCommerce product pages when they don't see proof that others have bought and loved what you sell. Adding real customer testimonials to your store — on product pages, your homepage, and checkout — turns browsers into buyers.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why WooCommerce stores need more than star ratings</h2>
      <p>Star ratings tell shoppers a product is good. Testimonials tell them <em>why</em> it's good and <em>who</em> it's for. A sentence like "I bought this as a gift for my mom and she uses it every single day" does more conversion work than a 4.8-star average. SocialProof helps you collect and display those human moments on any page of your WooCommerce store.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">High-converting testimonial placements for WooCommerce</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Product pages:</strong> Show buyer quotes directly under the add-to-cart button — highest-impact placement.</li>
        <li><strong>Homepage hero:</strong> Build brand trust before shoppers even browse products.</li>
        <li><strong>Category pages:</strong> Social proof at the browsing stage reduces bounce rate.</li>
        <li><strong>Cart/checkout page:</strong> Testimonials at checkout reduce abandonment from second-guessing.</li>
        <li><strong>Thank-you page:</strong> Reinforce the purchase decision, plant seeds for future reviews.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Easy embed, no developer needed</h2>
      <p>SocialProof generates a single JavaScript snippet. Paste it into any WooCommerce page via Elementor, Gutenberg, or your theme's custom HTML block. No plugin conflicts, no WooCommerce API required. Your widget loads fast and looks clean on any theme.</p>

      <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:3rem;text-align:center;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Add testimonials to your WooCommerce store today</h2>
        <p style="color:#555;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card required.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.9rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;">Get Started Free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
